<% if @organization.present? %>
Hello! @<%= @actor.display_login %> has created the new <%= @business.name %> Enterprise account on GitHub.
You’re a step closer to building better software, faster.

The <%= @organization.safe_profile_name %> organization has been added as the first
member organization in the new <%= @business.name %> enterprise.

- All previous owners of the <%= @organization.safe_profile_name %> organization are now
owners of the <%= @business.name %> enterprise.
- All previous billing managers of the <%= @organization.safe_profile_name %> organization
are now billing managers of the <%= @business.name %> enterprise.
<% else %>
Hi @<%= @actor.display_login %>!

Thank you for creating your GitHub Enterprise account, <%= @business.name %>.
You’re a step closer to building better software, faster.
<% end %>

To get started on your enterprise account now, follow this link:
<%= enterprise_url(@business) %>

We're here to help if you need it. Visit the Help Center at
<%= GitHub.help_url %>/github/setting-up-and-managing-your-enterprise/about-enterprise-accounts
to learn more about enterprise accounts or contact us at
https://github.com/enterprise/contact.

If you get a 404 page, make sure you’re signed in as an owner of <%= @business.name %>.
